## Markdown 演示：代码块 + SQL

```go
func ensureSession(cookie string) error {
  if strings.TrimSpace(cookie) == "" {
    return errors.New("session required")
  }
  return nil
}
```

```sql
SELECT id, role, expires_at
FROM auth_invite
WHERE revoked_at IS NULL
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 20;
```

结论：邀请码列表查询优先走索引字段，避免全表扫描。
